38
00:06:57,347 --> 00:07:01,443
I stvaranje Adama, Sunca, Meseca...

39
00:07:01,651 --> 00:07:03,209
- Postanje.

40
00:07:03,419 --> 00:07:08,652
Treba prekriti celu tavanicu.

41
00:07:08,858 --> 00:07:12,055
Evo mog plana:

42
