Vasa Svetosti,
Sad mozemo da napadnemo.

49
00:07:33,549 --> 00:07:34,914
Moramo!

50
00:07:37,053 --> 00:07:41,046
Koliko vremena?
- Nekoliko meseci, mozda godinu dana.

51
00:07:41,257 --> 00:07:43,987
Pet puta veci posao.
I novac?

52
00:07:44,193 --> 00:07:45,717
- Nece biti jeftino.

53
00:07:47,897 --> 00:07:49,990
Danas sam darezljiv,
Buonarroti.

54
00:07:50,199 --> 00:07:52,429
Dobices 4000 dukata.

55
00:07:52,635 --> 00:07:55,069
Za petostruko veci posao?
Ne mogu vise!

56
00:07:55,271 --> 00:07:57,501
Kostace me vise od 
opsade ovog grada!

57
00:07:57,707 --> 00:07:59,334
Trebace mi najmanje
10000 dukata,Vasa Svetosti.

58
00:07:59,542 --> 00:08:00,531
- Pet.
Osam!

59
00:08:00,743 --> 00:08:02,506
- sest hiljada i tacka!

60
00:08:02,712 --> 00:08:05,476
Cenjkas se sa papom?

61
00:08:06,382 --> 00:08:09,078
-Kako zelite,Sveti Oce.
-Onda 6000 dukata.

62
00:08:09,285 --> 00:08:11,845
Od njih placas stanarinu.

63
00:08:17,126 --> 00:08:19,151
Pozvaces pomocnike
iz Firence?

64
00:08:19,362 --> 00:08:21,922
Radicu sam.
To je jedini nacin.

65
00:08:22,131 --> 00:08:24,759
I zavrsices sve?
- Da.

66
00:08:24,968 --> 00:08:26,868
Siguran si?
- Jesam.

67
00:08:27,070 --> 00:08:29,436
Iako nisi slikar?

68
00:08:29,639 --> 00:08:31,903
Postacu.
-Dobro.

69
00:08:32,108 --> 00:08:33,666
- Na posao, sine.

70
00:08:33,876 --> 00:08:36,276
Dajte mu pratnju do Rima.
Tvoju licnu gardu.

71
00:08:36,479 --> 00:08:37,878
-Mora da stigne ziv.
-U redu,Vasa Svetosti.

72
00:08:38,081 --> 00:08:40,049
Ne mogu da napravim nesto
osrednje,

73
00:08:40,249 --> 00:08:43,946
mada ste to hteli.
-Niste to planirali.

74
00:08:44,153 --> 00:08:47,179
Ne. Ja sam planirao
tavanicu, a on cudo.

75
